; Regression test for issue #690: Add an option to output periodic transactions (BZ#690)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/690
; The --budget flag (and budget command) outputs periodic transactions alongside
; actual transactions, which implements the requested feature.

~ Monthly
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $80.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --budget -b 2024/01/01 -e 2024/03/01
24-Jan-01 Budget transaction    Expenses:Food              $-100.00     $-100.00
24-Jan-01 Budget transaction    Assets:Checking             $100.00            0
24-Jan-15 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $80.00       $80.00
                                Assets:Checking             $-80.00            0
24-Feb-01 Budget transaction    Expenses:Food              $-100.00     $-100.00
24-Feb-01 Budget transaction    Assets:Checking             $100.00            0
end test
